{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775847614854,"sessionID":"ses_2873ec91affe5CwFjLTC3zhF4t","part":{"id":"prt_d78c3490b001cA7Y9WDcxsKwdn","messageID":"msg_d78c33224001Ynb01leQ0OwV3u","sessionID":"ses_2873ec91affe5CwFjLTC3zhF4t","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_965ec373c87f4c38ac4885dd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-008/VERIFICATION_REPORT.md","content":"# AR-008 ŌĆö Sandbox GC Õ«ÜµŚČµĖģńÉåµ£║ÕłČ Verification Report\n\n## Summary\n\n**AR**: AR-008 ŌĆö Sandbox GC Õ«ÜµŚČµĖģńÉåµ£║ÕłČ  \n**Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language**: Go  \n**Size**: S  \n**Verification Date**: 2026-04-11  \n**Status**: Ō£ģ **MOSTLY COMPLIANT** (with noted gaps)\n\n---\n\n## Spec Requirements vs Implementation\n\n### 1. GC Core Implementation Ō£ģ\n\n| Spec Requirement | Implementation Status | Evidence |\n|-----------------|----------------------|----------|\n| `GarbageCollector` struct with config, client, store, context | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:32-38` |\n| Constructor `NewGarbageCollector()` | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:40-53` |\n| `Start()` method to run GC loop | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:55-58` |\n| `Stop()` method for graceful shutdown | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:60-63` |\n| `gcLoop()` with ticker-based scheduling | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:64-78` |\n| `tick()` method for GC scan | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:80-103` |\n\n**Analysis**: The GC core logic is implemented correctly with proper lifecycle management (Start/Stop), context-based cancellation, and ticker-driven periodic execution.\n\n---\n\n### 2. GC Policies & Configuration ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ\n\n| Spec Requirement | Implementation Status | Evidence |\n|-----------------|----------------------|----------|\n| Idle timeout detection | Ō£ģ Implemented | Uses `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15m` from `defaults.go:7` |\n| Expired sandbox detection | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:97-103` |\n| Configurable GC interval | Ō£ģ Implemented | `GCInterval = 15s` from `defaults.go:8`, passed to constructor |\n| Context timeout per tick | Ō£ģ Implemented | `GCSingleTickTimeout = 2m` from `defaults.go:9` |\n| Delete operation timeout | Ō£ģ Implemented | `DeleteTimeout = 30s` from `defaults.go:10` |\n| **Config struct for GC** | ŌØī **MISSING** | No `GCConfig` struct as specified in TASK-001 |\n| **MaxIdleCount enforcement** | ŌØī **MISSING** | No max idle count limit implemented |\n| **DryRun mode** | ŌØī **MISSING** | No dry-run capability |\n\n**Analysis**: Basic GC policies are implemented but the advanced configuration features from the tasks.md spec are missing (GCConfig, MaxIdleCount, DryRun).\n\n---\n\n### 3. Cleanup Mechanisms Ō£ģ\n\n| Spec Requirement | Implementation Status | Evidence |\n|-----------------|----------------------|----------|\n| Delete idle sandboxes (exceeding idle timeout) | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:86-94` |\n| Delete expired sandboxes | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:97-103` |\n| Support both AgentRuntime and SandboxClaim kinds | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:120-125` |\n| Store cleanup after K8s deletion | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:135-138` |\n| NotFound tolerance | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:132-134` |\n| Audit logging | Ō£ģ Implemented | `garbage_collector.go:147-152` |\n\n**Analysis**: The cleanup mechanism correctly handles both idle and expired sandboxes, with proper error handling for NotFound cases and audit trail logging.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Activity Tracking ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ\n\n| Spec Requirement | Implementation Status | Evidence |\n|-----------------|----------------------|----------|\n| Store last activity timestamp | Ō£ģ Implemented (in store) | Uses `LastActivityAt` field from `SandboxInfo` |\n| `ListInactiveSandboxes()` | Ō£ģ Implemented | Called from store client |\n| `ListExpiredSandboxes()` | Ō£ģ Implemented | Called from store client |\n| **Activity tracker middleware** | ŌØī **MISSING** | No `LastActivityTracker` as per TASK-020 |\n| **Activity integration with HTTP** | ŌØī **MISSING** | No middleware integration |\n\n**Analysis**: Activity tracking relies on the store interface but lacks the dedicated activity tracker and middleware integration specified in the tasks.\n\n---\n\n### 5. Metrics ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ\n\n| Spec Requirement | Implementation Status | Evidence |\n|-----------------|----------------------|----------|\n| **Prometheus metrics (gcRuns, gcDuration, etc.)** | ŌØī **MISSING** | No metrics implementation |\n| **GCMetrics struct** | ŌØī **MISSING** | No metrics struct |\n| **State counting** | ŌØī **MISSING** | No state-based gauges |\n\n**Analysis**: No metrics are currently exported. This is a significant gap for production monitoring.\n\n---\n\n### 6. State Management ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ\n\n| Spec Requirement | Implementation Status | Evidence |\n|-----------------|----------------------|----------|\n| **SandboxState enum (Active, Idle, Orphaned, Expired)** | ŌØī **MISSING** | No state enum defined |\n| **GCCandidate struct** | ŌØī **MISSING** | Uses `SandboxInfo` directly |\n| **evaluateState() method** | ŌØī **MISSING** | State evaluation is implicit in store queries |\n\n**Analysis**: The implementation takes a simpler approach by delegating state evaluation to the store layer rather than implementing explicit state machine logic.\n\n---\n\n### 7. Testing Ō£ģ\n\n| Test | Status | Location |\n|------|--------|----------|\n| `TestNewGarbageCollector` | Ō£ģ PASS | `garbage_collector_test.go:61-86` |\n| `TestGarbageCollector_StartStop` | Ō£ģ PASS | `garbage_collector_test.go:88-99` |\n| `TestGarbageCollector_Tick_IdleCleanup` | Ō£ģ PASS | `garbage_collector_test.go:101-122` |\n| `TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ExpiredCleanup` | Ō£ģ PASS | `garbage_collector_test.go:124-147` |\n| `TestGarbageCollector_DeleteSandbox_NotFound` | Ō£ģ PASS | `garbage_collector_test.go:149-168` |\n| `TestGarbageCollector_DeleteSandbox_StoreError` | Ō£ģ PASS | `garbage_collector_test.go:170-189` |\n| `TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ContextTimeout` | Ō£ģ PASS | `garbage_collector_test.go:191-210` |\n| `TestGarbageCollector_Tick_StoreError` | Ō£ģ PASS | `garbage_collector_test.go:212-224` |\n\n**Test Coverage**: 8 passing tests covering construction, lifecycle, idle cleanup, expired cleanup, error handling, and timeout scenarios.\n\n**Missing Tests** (per tasks.md):\n- ŌØī Activity tracker tests (TASK-020 to TASK-023)\n- ŌØī Metrics tests (TASK-030 to TASK-032)\n- ŌØī Integration tests (TEST-050, TEST-051)\n- ŌØĀ MaxIdleCount tests (depends on missing feature)\n- ŌØĀ DryRun tests (depends on missing feature)\n\n---\n\n### 8. client-go Library Verification ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ\n\nThe spec references a generated `client-go` library at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`. **This directory does not exist** in the current workspace.\n\n| Spec Component | Status |\n|---------------|--------|\n| `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | ŌØī Not found |\n| `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | ŌØī Not found |\n| `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | ŌØī Not found |\n| `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | ŌØī Not found |\n| `informers/externalversions/factory.go` | ŌØī Not found |\n| `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/` | ŌØī Not found |\n| Fake clients | ŌØī Not found |\n\n**Analysis**: The client-go library has not been generated yet. The GC implementation uses `dynamic.Interface` instead of the typed client, which works but doesn't match the spec's architecture.\n\n---\n\n### 9. Configuration Integration ŌØī\n\n| Spec Requirement | Status |\n|-----------------|--------|\n| GC flags in `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` | ŌØī Missing (no cmd directory found) |\n| Environment variables (`GC_ENABLED`, `GC_INTERVAL`, etc.) | ŌØī Not documented or used |\n| Integration with main startup | ŌØī Not visible |\n\n**Analysis**: No integration with the main entry point is visible. The GC can be constructed but there's no evidence of it being wired into the application startup.\n\n---\n\n### 10. Documentation ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ\n\n| Requirement | Status |\n|------------|--------|\n| Package documentation (`doc.go`) | ŌØī Missing |\n| Godoc comments on public types | ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ Partial (some comments present) |\n| README update | ŌØī Not in `changes/AR-008/` |\n\n---\n\n## Gaps Summary\n\n### Critical Gaps (P0)\n1. **client-go library not generated** - The spec assumes a typed client that doesn't exist\n2. **No main integration** - GC is not wired into application startup\n3. **No metrics** - Production monitoring capability missing\n\n### High Priority Gaps (P1)\n4. **Missing GCConfig** - Configuration is hardcoded rather than configurable\n5. **No MaxIdleCount enforcement** - Cannot limit number of idle sandboxes\n6. **No DryRun mode** - Cannot test GC without actual deletion\n7. **No activity tracker middleware** - Activity tracking is passive\n\n### Medium Priority Gaps (P2)\n8. **Missing state machine** - No explicit SandboxState enum or evaluation\n9. **Incomplete documentation** - Missing package docs and godoc comments\n10. **No integration tests** - Only unit tests present\n\n---\n\n## Test Results Summary\n\n```\nPackage: github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager\nGC Tests: 8/8 PASS\nCoverage: ~43% (module-wide, includes non-GC code)\n```\n\n**Passing Tests**:\n- Ō£ģ TestNewGarbageCollector\n- Ō£ģ TestGarbageCollector_StartStop\n- Ō£ģ TestGarbageCollector_Tick_IdleCleanup\n- Ō£ģ TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ExpiredCleanup\n- Ō£ģ TestGarbageCollector_DeleteSandbox_NotFound\n- Ō£ģ TestGarbageCollector_DeleteSandbox_StoreError\n- Ō£ģ TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ContextTimeout\n- Ō£ģ TestGarbageCollector_Tick_StoreError\n\n**Failing Tests** (in related packages):\n- ŌØī TestBuildSandboxObject (processor package - unrelated to GC)\n- ŌØī TestBuildCodeInterpreterSandbox (processor package - unrelated to GC)\n- ŌØī reconciler package build failure (missing json import)\n\n---\n\n## Compliance Matrix\n\n| Category | Requirements Met | Total | Compliance |\n|----------|-----------------|-------|------------|\n| Core GC Logic | 6/6 | 6 | 100% Ō£ģ |\n| GC Policies | 5/8 | 8 | 62% ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ |\n| Cleanup Mechanisms | 6/6 | 6 | 100% Ō£ģ |\n| Activity Tracking | 2/4 | 4 | 50% ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ |\n| Metrics | 0/4 | 4 | 0% ŌØī |\n| State Management | 0/3 | 3 | 0% ŌØī |\n| Testing | 8/13 | 13 | 62% ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ |\n| client-go Library | 0/7 | 7 | 0% ŌØī |\n| Configuration | 0/3 | 3 | 0% ŌØī |\n| Documentation | 1/3 | 3 | 33% ŌØī |\n| **OVERALL** | **28/57** | **57** | **49%** ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ |\n\n---\n\n## Recommendations\n\n### Immediate Actions (Required for Spec Compliance)\n1. **Generate client-go library**: Run `make gen-client` to generate typed clients\n2. **Wire GC into main**: Integrate GC startup/shutdown with application lifecycle\n3. **Add GCConfig**: Create configuration struct with flags/env vars\n\n### Short-term Improvements\n4. **Implement metrics**: Add Prometheus metrics for GC operations\n5. **Add MaxIdleCount**: Implement idle sandbox count limiting\n6. **Add DryRun mode**: Enable safe testing of GC policies\n\n### Long-term Enhancements\n7. **State machine**: Explicit state tracking and evaluation\n8. **Activity middleware**: HTTP middleware for activity tracking\n9. **Integration tests**: End-to-end tests with real Kubernetes\n10. **Documentation**: Complete godoc and user documentation\n\n---\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThe AR-008 implementation provides a **functional but incomplete** sandbox garbage collection mechanism. The core GC logic is solid with proper lifecycle management, idle/expired sandbox detection, and comprehensive unit tests. However, significant gaps exist in:\n\n- Generated client-go library (completely missing)\n- Application integration (not wired into main)\n- Advanced features (metrics, config, dry-run, max idle count)\n- Documentation\n\n**Verdict**: The implementation satisfies the **minimum viable product** for GC functionality but does not fully comply with the detailed specification in `tasks.md`. Priority should be given to generating the client-go library, integrating GC into the application, and adding metrics for production readiness.\n\n---\n\n## Appendix: File Locations\n\n### Implemented Files\n- `/pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - Core GC implementation\n- `/pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go` - Unit tests\n- `/pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go` - GC constants\n- `/pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types.go` - Sandbox data structures\n\n### Missing Files (per spec)\n- `/client-go/` - Generated client library\n- `/pkg/workloadmanager/gc/config.go` - GC configuration\n- `/pkg/workloadmanager/gc/state.go` - State definitions\n- `/pkg/workloadmanager/gc/candidate.go` - GCCandidate type\n- `/pkg/workloadmanager/gc/activity.go` - Activity tracker\n- `/pkg/workloadmanager/gc/metrics.go` - Metrics implementation\n- `/cmd/workload-manager/main.go` - Application entry point\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler.go\">\nERROR [166:12] undefined: json\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/config.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/work